        <description>&lt;p&gt;Hello! My name is &lt;strong&gt;Kauã Moreno&lt;/strong&gt;, and this is &lt;strong&gt;Moreno&amp;rsquo;s Blog&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I’m a Information Systems student at USP, and I created this blog as a place to document my learning, share experiments, and record things I’m studying or building throughout my journey in technology.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here you will mainly find posts about:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Backend&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Web Development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Linux&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cybersecurity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The idea is to use this space as a kind of technical journal, where I write about knowledge, notes, experiments, and projects. Besides helping me organize what I’m learning, I also hope the content can be useful to other people studying technology.&lt;/p&gt;
